snippet: A series of attacks, including in the secured government area, rocked the Iraqi capital, while violence continued in restive Anbar Province.
abstract: Two rockets slam into international zone in Baghdad, killing soldier; wave of bombings in other parts of city kill fifteen people.
lead_paragraph: A series of attacks, including in the secured government area, rocked the Iraqi capital, while violence continued in restive Anbar Province.

headline.main: More Than a Dozen Killed in Attacks in Baghdad Area
headline.print_headline: Iraq: Rockets and Bombs Hit Baghdad
